	<text xml:lang="de">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Siderhar ich den vorigen brieff verschlossen, verstan ich, das ein tag den 4 stetten, Zürych, <placeName ref="l41" cert="high">Bernn</placeName>, <placeName ref="l28" cert="high">Basel</placeName> und <placeName ref="l441" cert="high">Schaffhusen</placeName>, beschriben wirt sontag über 8 tag zuͦ <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2" cert="high">Aaraw</placeName> etc.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Hiemitt schicken ich üch die urteyl, fast ungegrünt, wider h[erren] <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p7458" cert="high">Egmonden</persName>.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Datum in yl, gott mitt üch, <foreign xml:lang="la">ut in literis.</foreign></s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Dem frommen, eerenvesten herren <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p252" cert="high"><persName type="citizen_name" ref="p252">Jochimen Beldi</persName></persName>, allten landtamen zuͦ <placeName ref="l646" cert="high">Glaris</placeName>, minem günstigen, lieben herren.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l646" cert="high">Glaris</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note><persName type="citizen_name" ref="p7458" cert="high">Egmont</persName>'s Hinrichtung: Juni 1568; Tag in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2" cert="high">Aarau</placeName>: 9. Aug. 1568 (<bibl>EA</bibl> IV/2, 393).</note>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
	</text>
